      <title>穆迪因财政和政治风险下调斯洛伐克信用评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/slovakia-s-rating-cut-at-moody-s-on-fiscal-and-political-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪评级将斯洛伐克的主权信用评分下调了一个等级，理由是担心政治紧张局势和国家债务恶化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/slovakia-s-rating-cut-at-moody-s-on-fiscal-and-political-risks</guid>
